再出黎呃飲呃食啦</blockquote><br />\n佢係平行時空既香港書展做生意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9c626be46d4bc112841a1adbaf377716903f9e","tid":335581,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T19:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/003605_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F003605_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg&h=9c93e31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更再一次教曉我們，腳踏實地，何其重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好心條垃圾唔好再出黎呃飲呃食啦</blockquote><br />\n佢係平行時空既香港書展做生意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時光機<br />\n返一年前"},{"pid":"a83ec245f7154801fcb011a099c34a4277131d4b","tid":335581,"uid":52002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T19:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/003605_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F003605_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg&h=9c93e31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更再一次教曉我們，腳踏實地，何其重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好心條垃圾唔好再出黎呃飲呃食啦</blockquote><br />\n佢係平行時空既香港書展做生意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時光機<br />\n返一年前</blockquote><br />\n上年好似無花生友喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係果個平行時空<br />\n熱狗踢爆黃毓民收共產黨錢、有真憑實據，原本黃毓民既支持者幾乎全部過檔<br />\n黃毓民變成過街老鼠，負政治能量既老人家<br />\n佢只可以派出打手仇思達，同佢既支持者去騷擾熱狗做生意，但無用<br />\n作為宇宙唯一港獨派，熱狗著作大行其道；普羅蝕到就黎搭車都無錢，要問共產黨攞<br />\n<br />\n可能黃洋達自己就俾咁樣FF<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369ace479ed9de49f9e6288b898a47c8ac3c5807","tid":335581,"uid":43085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T21:13:53.000Z","msg":"邊撚度有人攪過佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食熱狗果單野都係你老婆衝出黎柒, 怪得邊個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到尾又係叫人課金, 課課課課你老母咩,<br />\n正正經經搵份工啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87fb5cce0068277f68b038b529e5ef4da0d4772","tid":335581,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/004232_d41f41fa8c19d710efdc9ffc525d95bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F004232_d41f41fa8c19d710efdc9ffc525d95bc.jpg&h=a8dd05de&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己唔敢開名, 一有人開名, 佢又叫人唔好講呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46af23329c21f5c4ae6fbf3cdcf8e138dc0127d2","tid":335581,"uid":5292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/004232_d41f41fa8c19d710efdc9ffc525d95bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F004232_d41f41fa8c19d710efdc9ffc525d95bc.jpg&h=a8dd05de&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n自爆？"},{"pid":"c97210c23a09984f8ec28bc54563ded706f21907","tid":335581,"uid":130974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:09:13.000Z","msg":"佢個檔好似成日無乜人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0728f75e3054c426b9223802223a2c508fc31c6d","tid":335581,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:53:09.0